22  Menya ũkaahinyĩrĩria mũthĩĩni tondũ wĩ na ũhoti wa gwĩka ũguo,

kana ũhinyĩrĩrie mũndũ ũtarĩ na hinya mwĩ ciirainĩ naake.


23  Nĩ amu MWATHANI nĩ we ũgatuĩka wa kũmaarĩrĩria,

na amarĩhĩrie harĩ arĩa maramahinyĩrĩria.

-
2  -


24  Ndũkaanatume ndũgũ na mũndũ ũhiũhaga kũraakara,

kana ũthiĩ rũgendo na mũndũ wa mang'ũrĩ,


25  nĩ geetha ndũkaae kũnyiita mĩtugo yake,

mũtũũrĩre waku ũgĩthũũkane.

-
3  -


26  Ndũkaanatuĩke wa kũrũũgamĩrĩra mũndũ agĩkomba thiirĩ.


27  Ũngĩgaakĩaga gĩa kũrĩha nakĩo,

ũgaatuunywo o na ũrĩrĩ ũrĩa ũkomagĩra.

-
4  -


28  Menya gũkaanakũũra mũtĩ wa tene wa mũhaka

ũrĩa maathooguo maahandire.

-
5  -


29  Mũruti wa wĩra wĩ kĩyo-rĩ, ũcio no atuĩke wa gũtwaranaga na mũthamaki,

ti wa gũtwaranaga na tũmũndũ o ũguo tũtarĩ kĩene.

